# FlowAnalyzer

# Installation

Install the package using pip:

```
pip3 insatll FlowAnalyzer
```

# Usage

```
$ git clone https://github.com/Byxs20/FlowAnalyzer.git
$ cd ./FlowAnalyzer/
```
